Heat grill to medium-high heat. Toss vegetables with dressing. Grill 5 to 8 min. or until crisp-tender, turning occasionally. Remove from grill. Cut peppers into thin strips; cut zucchini and onions into 3/4-inch pieces. Mix cream cheese and pesto; spread onto pitas. Top with vegetables and shredded cheese. Grill 3 to 5 min. or until shredded cheese is melted